<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Sample responses:</p>
<ol>
      <li>The second triangle is larger because it is taller. The first one is larger because it is longer.</li>
      <li><ol>
<li>The second oval is larger. I can fit the first one inside it.</li>
<li>The hexagon is larger. The triangle is less than half the size.</li>
<li>The first rectangle is larger. I can fit the second one inside it if I cut it in half and put the halves next to each other.</li>
</ol>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </solution>


